《'''24小時觸目驚心'''》（{{lang-en|''24 Hour Psycho''}}）是一部由英國藝術家{{link-en|道格拉斯·戈登|Douglas Gordon}}於1993年創作的[[裝置藝術|裝置藝術]]。戈登把[[希治閣|希治閣]]的恐怖電影《[[觸目驚心|觸目驚心]]》以每秒兩幀的速度重新播放，使得原來片長109分鐘的電影變成1440分鐘，即整整24小時<ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F02E1D81431F932A25755C0A9609C8B63|title=THE WEEK AHEAD: June 11 - June 17; FILM|last=Lee|first=Nathan|date=11 June 2006|work=The New York Times|accessdate=16 November 2009|archive-date=2015-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118131429/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F02E1D81431F932A25755C0A9609C8B63|dead-url=no}}</ref>。戈登解釋此作的用意是「讓觀者從眼前所見的事物引發腦海中回憶，來探索想像與回憶共同編織成的視覺記憶」，因事情在過去一段時間後，印象也會漸漸模糊起來<ref>{{cite news|url=http://arts.guardian.co.uk/pictures/image/0,8543,-10104531576,00.html|title=Douglas Gordon: what have i done|work=The Guardian|accessdate=16 November 2009|archive-date=2013-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130610003457/http://arts.guardian.co.uk/pictures/image/0,8543,-10104531576,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

